Creates a kindle ebook in MOBI format from some confluence markup content.

It uses wikitext first to create HTML from confluence markup.
Secondly it uses kindlegen to create an ebook from HTML.

kindlegen must be installed on your local machine. See src/main/shell/kindlegen.sh

After running
# mvn package
the ebook can hopefully be found in directory
target/kindle

Ready to be uploaded to amazon.


